text={
[1]={
ja={
{
"魂人が織りなす光は、いつしか夕陽の光に移り変わった。",
},
},
en={
{
"The lights weaved by the tamabito eventually shifted to those of twilight.",
},
},
},
[2]={
ja={
{
"放課後を迎えた学校に、ひとりの男性教諭が現れた。",
},
},
en={
{
"With the school day over, a certain male teacher paid a surprise visit to the school.",
},
},
},
[3]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00191",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「失礼します」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Pardon my entrance.」",
},
},
},
[4]={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rei_00471",ch="fem"},
},
name={name="玲子",ja="玲子",en="Reiko"},
ja={
{
"「砂原……？」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Sahara...?」",
},
},
},
[5]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00192",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「どうしました、学園長。鳩が豆鉄砲を食らったようなお顔をして」",
},
},
en={
{
"「What's the matter? You look like you've seen a ghost.」",
},
},
},
[6]={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rei_00472",ch="fem"},
},
name={name="玲子",ja="玲子",en="Reiko"},
ja={
{
"「……おまえも、還ったのだと思っていたからな」",
},
},
en={
{
"「...I thought you had returned.」",
},
},
},
[7]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00193",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「まだ、還ることはできませんよ」",
},
},
en={
{
"「No, I can't go yet.」",
},
},
},
[8]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00194",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「学園長に別れのあいさつをしていないのですから……」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Not without giving you my farewells...」",
},
},
},
[9]={
ja={
{
"砂原は先日、山代に襲われたこともあった。",
},
},
en={
{
"Sahara was attacked by Yamashiro the other day.",
},
},
},
[10]={
ja={
{
"だが、そのときはうまく逃げおおせた。",
},
},
en={
{
"But he had managed to get away.",
},
},
},
[11]={
ja={
{
"土砂を操る砂原の奇跡は、身を守る術には事欠かない。",
},
},
en={
{
"His control over sand provided excellent means for defending himself.",
},
},
},
[12]={
ja={
{
"そもそも、山代にも迷いがあった。その躊躇が、",
{"ruby",text="とりもの"},
"採物",
{"/ruby"},
"を操る手を鈍くさせた。",
},
},
en={
{
"Yamashiro was in doubt at the time, and that hesitation dulled his spear arm.",
},
},
},
[13]={
ja={
{
"だから砂原は、こうして学園長に会いに来ることができた。",
},
},
en={
{
"Thus, Sahara managed to make his way back to Reiko.",
},
},
},
[14]={
ja={
{
"辞表を提出することができたのだ。",
},
},
en={
{
"So he could hand in his resignation.",
},
},
},
[15]={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rei_00473",ch="fem"},
},
name={name="玲子",ja="玲子",en="Reiko"},
ja={
{
"「……そうか」",
},
},
en={
{
"「...I see.」",
},
},
},
[16]={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rei_00474",ch="fem"},
},
name={name="玲子",ja="玲子",en="Reiko"},
ja={
{
"「これが、別れのあいさつか」",
},
},
en={
{
"「So this is goodbye.」",
},
},
},
[17]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00195",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「はい」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Yes.」",
},
},
},
[18]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00196",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「学園長。これまで、ありがとうございました」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Madam Principal. Thank you for everything you've done.」",
},
},
},
[19]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00197",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「あなたのおかげで、僕は幸せに還ることができます」",
},
},
en={
{
"「It's because of you that I can return in happiness.」",
},
},
},
[20]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00198",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「最期に、彩香女子学園と富野学園を、見て回ろうと思っています」",
},
},
en={
{
"「I think I'll take one last look at Saika Girls Academy and Tomino Academy before I go.」",
},
},
},
[21]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00199",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「下校する生徒たちにも、あいさつをしてきます」",
},
},
en={
{
"「To greet the students on their way home.」",
},
},
},
[22]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00200",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「さようなら……と」",
},
},
en={
{
"「And tell them goodbye...」",
},
},
},
[23]={
ja={
{
"砂原は一礼し、去っていく。",
},
},
en={
{
"Sahara departed with a bow.",
},
},
},
[24]={
ja={
{
"その動作には、一切の躊躇もない。",
},
},
en={
{
"There wasn't a hint of hesitation to be seen.",
},
},
},
[25]={
ja={
{
"だから玲子は、声すらかけられず……。",
},
},
en={
{
"So Reiko wordlessly saw him off...",
},
},
},
[26]={
ja={
{
"今までの自分なら、そうだっただろう……。",
},
},
en={
{
"Or at least, the her from yesterday would have...",
},
},
},
[27]={
ja={
{
"目の前で還っていった最愛の夫にすら、まともに声をかけられなかった自分なのだから……。",
},
},
en={
{
"Like how she couldn't say a thing when her husband left right before her eyes...",
},
},
},
[28]={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rei_00475",ch="fem"},
},
name={name="玲子",ja="玲子",en="Reiko"},
ja={
{
"「砂原……！」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Sahara...!」",
},
},
},
[29]={
ja={
{
"玲子の中に、突き動かすなにかが生まれた。",
},
},
en={
{
"Something within spurred her into action.",
},
},
},
[30]={
ja={
{
"そのなにかはきっと、この町が培ってくれたものだった。",
},
},
en={
{
"She knew that it was something the town cultivated in her.",
},
},
},
[31]={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rei_00476",ch="fem"},
},
name={name="玲子",ja="玲子",en="Reiko"},
ja={
{
"「砂原……おまえは、最高のパートナーだった」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Sahara... you were the best partner I could have asked for.」",
},
},
},
[32]={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rei_00477",ch="fem"},
},
name={name="玲子",ja="玲子",en="Reiko"},
ja={
{
"「先に逝け……私も、いつか追いかける」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Go on... I'll join you some day.」",
},
},
},
[33]={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rei_00478",ch="fem"},
},
name={name="玲子",ja="玲子",en="Reiko"},
ja={
{
"「空の上での再会を……楽しみにしているよ」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Let's meet again... beyond the heavens.」",
},
},
},
[34]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00201",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「……はい」",
},
},
en={
{
"「...Yes.」",
},
},
},
[35]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00202",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「僕も、楽しみに待っています」",
},
},
en={
{
"「I'll be waiting.」",
},
},
},
[36]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00203",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「そのときは、お酒でも飲みましょう」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Let's go out for drinks when that time comes.」",
},
},
},
[37]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00204",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「学園長……いえ、玲子さん」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Madam Principal... no, Reiko-san.」",
},
},
},
[38]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00205",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「それまでに、下戸から卒業しておいてくださいよ」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Try to build up your alcohol resistance until then.」",
},
},
},
[39]={
ja={
{
"砂原は、笑顔で立ち去った。",
},
},
en={
{
"Sahara left with a smile.",
},
},
},
[40]={
ja={
{
"玲子も、笑顔で見送った。",
},
},
en={
{
"And Reiko saw him off smiling.",
},
},
},
[41]={
ja={
{
"どちらの笑みもぎこちないものだった。",
},
},
en={
{
"Both were strained and awkward.",
},
},
},
[42]={
ja={
{
"必死に耐えるような作り笑みだった。",
},
},
en={
{
"Forced smiles to hold back their tears.",
},
},
},
[43]={
ja={
{
"だからこそ、その表情は、この世で最も尊かった。",
},
},
en={
{
"But that's what made them so sacred.",
},
},
},
[44]={
ja={
{
"夕空に、一番星のような光が瞬き、消えていった。",
},
},
en={
{
"A light flickered in the sky like the first star of evening, and vanished.",
},
},
},
},
label={
},
}
